paws 0.1.3

Returns the current configuration items for resources that are present in your AWS Config aggregator

Source: R/configservice_operations.R
configservice_batch_get_aggregate_resource_config.Rd

Returns the current configuration items for resources that are present in your AWS Config aggregator. The operation also returns a list of resources that are not processed in the current request. If there are no unprocessed resources, the operation returns an empty unprocessedResourceIdentifiers list.

configservice_batch_get_aggregate_resource_config(
  ConfigurationAggregatorName, ResourceIdentifiers)

Arguments

ConfigurationAggregatorName

[required] The name of the configuration aggregator.
ResourceIdentifiers

[required] A list of aggregate ResourceIdentifiers objects.

Details

  • The API does not return results for deleted resources.

  • The API does not return tags and relationships.
